      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 61 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 61 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>中孚，豚魚吉，利涉大川，利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Zhong Fu (moves even) pigs and fish, and leads to good fortune. There will be advantage in crossing the great stream. There will be advantage in being firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
