      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 61 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 61 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：虞吉，有他不燕。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I. The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject resting (in himself). There will be good fortune. If he sought to any other, he would not find rest.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
