      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 61 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 61 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：鳴鶴在陰，其子和之，我有好爵，吾與爾靡之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject (like) the crane crying out in her hidden retirement, and her young ones responding to her. (It is as if it were said), 'I have a cup of good spirits,' (and the response were), 'I will partake of it with you.'</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
