      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 61 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：得敵，或鼓或罷，或泣或歌。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject having met with his mate. Now he beats his drum, and now he leaves off. Now he weeps, and now he sings.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
