      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：月几望，馬匹亡，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject (like) the moon nearly full, and (like) a horse (in a chariot) whose fellow disappears. There will be no error.</seg>
