        <seg>上九：翰音登于天，貞凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows its subject in chanticleer (trying to) mount to heaven. Even with firm correctness there will be evil.</seg>
